- (start) Initialize project analysis workflow
 - Read project structure with ls command
 - Identify main entry point file
 - Analyze dependencies and imports
 - (analyze) Review package configuration
 - Check for test coverage reports
 - Generate architecture diagram notes
- (validate) Validate findings
 - Compare structure with expected layout
 - Document deviations or concerns
 - Prepare summary report for review
- @validate[1]: Requirements met
- (report) Generate final analysis
 - Include dependency graph
 - List potential improvements
 - Suggest refactoring opportunities
 - Export findings to documentation
- @analyze[2]: Need deeper inspection
- Complete workflow execution now
